title: Week 17 Preview, Playoff Predictions (Football 12/27)
description:
Will Brinson and Jason La Canfora talk about what they saw in week 16, what's to come in the last week of the regular season and who they foresee going to the postseason. First, the guys talk about what teams are in and out of playoff contention after the week 16 results. Next, they preview what's ahead on the Week 17 slate of games. Then, the duo talk about teams that may rest their starters and the New Year's Eve night game getting canceled. Finally, the Dallas Cowboys come up once again on whether or not a coaching change is what's needed.
